{
  "title": "CentOS 6.6 如何启用中文输入法",
  "cells": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<div style=\"position: relative;\"><embed id=\"xunlei_com_thunder_helper_plugin_d462f475-c18e-46be-bd10-327458d045bd\" type=\"application/thunder_download_plugin\" height=\"0\" width=\"0\"><span style=\"text-align: justify; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px;\">安装CentOS系统后，如何启用中文输入法呢？这个问题看起来简单，但对于Linux初学者来说，也可能不是一件容易的事。本文笔者和大家分享一下“CentOS 6.6 如何启用中文输入法”的经验，希望能对大家有所帮助！</span><div class=\"exp-content-block\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; margin-top: 40px;\"><h2 class=\"exp-content-head\" style=\"margin: 40px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(214, 214, 216);\"><a name=\"section-2\" style=\"color: rgb(45, 100, 179);\"></a>工具/原料</h2><div class=\"exp-content-body\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-top: 5px;\"><ul class=\"exp-content-unorderlist \" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; clear: both;\"><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 25px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/iknow/exp/global/unsortlist.png); background-attachment: scroll; background-position: 0px 8px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"><div class=\"content-list-text\">安装了CentOS系统的电脑</div></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"exp-content-block\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 16px; line-height: 28px; margin-top: 40px;\"><h2 class=\"exp-content-head\" style=\"margin: 40px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 7px; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 24px; font-family: 微软雅黑; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(214, 214, 216);\"><a name=\"section-3\" style=\"color: rgb(45, 100, 179);\"></a>方法/步骤</h2><div class=\"exp-content-body\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-top: 5px;\"><ol class=\"exp-conent-orderlist\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; list-style: none; clear: both;\"><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-1\" style=\"margin: 20px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 35px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; border-left-width: 2px; border-left-style: dotted; border-left-color: rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><div class=\"list-icon\" style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; position: absolute; left: -18px; top: 0px; color: rgb(238, 255, 238); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/iknow/exp/global/step_ol_bg.png); visibility: hidden; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"></div><div class=\"content-list-text\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">首先要确保系统中已经安装了中文输入法。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">如果你在安装系统时选择了中文，则中文输入法默认就会安装；如果你安装时选择了英文，则必须在安装时选择安装中文输入法，否则不会安装，即使你忘了选择，还是可以在装好系统之后安装。安装方法也非常简单，只需要联网后执行</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">【sudo yum install \"@Chinese Support\"】命令即可安装，如下图所示：</p></div><div class=\"content-list-media\"><div class=\"content-list-image clearfix\" style=\"zoom: 1; position: relative; padding: 10px 0px;\"><a class=\"exp-image-wraper\" href=\"http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/da1091fb3e7f8a027849d681.html?picindex=1\" target=\"_self\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(45, 100, 179); position: relative; display: block; float: left;\"><img class=\"exp-image-default\" alt=\"CentOS 6.6 如何启用中文输入法\" src=\"quiver-image-url/ED42EABBFEBE134DF5E80A8095EC6C55.png\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block;\" width=\"375\" height=\"243\"><span class=\"exp-album-enter-mask\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); opacity: 0; cursor: pointer;\"></span></a></div></div></li><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-2\" style=\"margin: 1px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 45px 0px 0px 35px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; border-left-width: 2px; border-left-style: dotted; border-left-color: rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><div class=\"list-icon\" style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; position: absolute; left: -18px; top: 43px; color: rgb(238, 255, 238); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/iknow/exp/global/step_ol_bg.png); visibility: hidden; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"></div><div class=\"content-list-text\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">接下来是启用中文输入法的操作。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">依次单击【系统】---&gt;【首选项】---&gt;【输入法】,如下图所示：</p></div><div class=\"content-list-media\"><div class=\"content-list-image clearfix\" style=\"zoom: 1; position: relative; padding: 10px 0px;\"><a class=\"exp-image-wraper\" href=\"http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/da1091fb3e7f8a027849d681.html?picindex=2\" target=\"_self\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(45, 100, 179); position: relative; display: block; float: left;\"><img class=\"exp-image-default\" alt=\"CentOS 6.6 如何启用中文输入法\" src=\"quiver-image-url/1C94D9E966D0CE5C006B49972061642B.png\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block;\" width=\"375\" height=\"304\"><span class=\"exp-album-enter-mask\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); opacity: 0; cursor: pointer;\"></span></a></div></div></li><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-3\" style=\"margin: 1px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 45px 0px 0px 35px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; border-left-width: 2px; border-left-style: dotted; border-left-color: rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><div class=\"list-icon\" style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; position: absolute; left: -18px; top: 43px; color: rgb(238, 255, 238); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/iknow/exp/global/step_ol_bg.png); visibility: hidden; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"></div><div class=\"content-list-text\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">在弹出的对话框中勾选【启动输入法特性】选项，如下图所示：</p></div><div class=\"content-list-media\"><div class=\"content-list-image clearfix\" style=\"zoom: 1; position: relative; padding: 10px 0px;\"><a class=\"exp-image-wraper\" href=\"http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/da1091fb3e7f8a027849d681.html?picindex=3\" target=\"_self\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(45, 100, 179); position: relative; display: block; float: left;\"><img class=\"exp-image-default\" alt=\"CentOS 6.6 如何启用中文输入法\" src=\"quiver-image-url/8E394E30DC0F171EABCEC91B66F4930B.png\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block;\" width=\"375\" height=\"289\"><span class=\"exp-album-enter-mask\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); opacity: 0; cursor: pointer;\"></span></a></div></div></li><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-4\" style=\"margin: 1px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 45px 0px 0px 35px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; border-left-width: 2px; border-left-style: dotted; border-left-color: rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><div class=\"list-icon\" style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; position: absolute; left: -18px; top: 43px; color: rgb(238, 255, 238); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/iknow/exp/global/step_ol_bg.png); visibility: hidden; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"></div><div class=\"content-list-text\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">此时中文输入法就已经被启用了，接下来看一下有哪些中文输入法。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">单击【首先输入法】命令，如下图所示：</p></div><div class=\"content-list-media\"><div class=\"content-list-image clearfix\" style=\"zoom: 1; position: relative; padding: 10px 0px;\"><a class=\"exp-image-wraper\" href=\"http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/da1091fb3e7f8a027849d681.html?picindex=4\" target=\"_self\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(45, 100, 179); position: relative; display: block; float: left;\"><img class=\"exp-image-default\" alt=\"CentOS 6.6 如何启用中文输入法\" src=\"quiver-image-url/5AD7686C0ABF48B6AC87E448BF65DD98.png\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block;\" width=\"375\" height=\"274\"><span class=\"exp-album-enter-mask\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); opacity: 0; cursor: pointer;\"></span></a></div></div></li><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-5\" style=\"margin: 1px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 45px 0px 0px 35px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; border-left-width: 2px; border-left-style: dotted; border-left-color: rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><div class=\"list-icon\" style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; position: absolute; left: -18px; top: 43px; color: rgb(238, 255, 238); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/iknow/exp/global/step_ol_bg.png); visibility: hidden; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"></div><div class=\"content-list-text\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">在“iBus设置”对话框中，单击【输入法】，如下图所示：</p></div><div class=\"content-list-media\"><div class=\"content-list-image clearfix\" style=\"zoom: 1; position: relative; padding: 10px 0px;\"><a class=\"exp-image-wraper\" href=\"http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/da1091fb3e7f8a027849d681.html?picindex=5\" target=\"_self\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(45, 100, 179); position: relative; display: block; float: left;\"><img class=\"exp-image-default\" alt=\"CentOS 6.6 如何启用中文输入法\" src=\"quiver-image-url/0F28C0F0A95E25EB383A440A03D3717C.png\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block;\" width=\"375\" height=\"294\"><span class=\"exp-album-enter-mask\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); opacity: 0; cursor: pointer;\"></span></a></div></div></li><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-6\" style=\"margin: 1px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 45px 0px 0px 35px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; border-left-width: 2px; border-left-style: dotted; border-left-color: rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><div class=\"list-icon\" style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; position: absolute; left: -18px; top: 43px; color: rgb(238, 255, 238); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/iknow/exp/global/step_ol_bg.png); visibility: hidden; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"></div><div class=\"content-list-text\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">可以看到系统已经预选了三种输入法，其中的【汉语-Pinyin】是我们要用的输入法。</p></div><div class=\"content-list-media\"><div class=\"content-list-image clearfix\" style=\"zoom: 1; position: relative; padding: 10px 0px;\"><a class=\"exp-image-wraper\" href=\"http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/da1091fb3e7f8a027849d681.html?picindex=6\" target=\"_self\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(45, 100, 179); position: relative; display: block; float: left;\"><img class=\"exp-image-default\" alt=\"CentOS 6.6 如何启用中文输入法\" src=\"quiver-image-url/186F22B2CA0DF2B3111300B08886D63A.png\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block;\" width=\"375\" height=\"275\"><span class=\"exp-album-enter-mask\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); opacity: 0; cursor: pointer;\"></span></a></div></div></li><li class=\"exp-content-list list-item-7\" style=\"margin: 1px 0px 0px 17px; padding: 45px 0px 0px 35px; display: block; position: relative; min-height: 31px; border-left-width: 2px; border-left-style: dotted; border-left-color: rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><div class=\"list-icon\" style=\"width: 32px; height: 32px; position: absolute; left: -18px; top: 43px; color: rgb(238, 255, 238); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; background-image: url(http://img.baidu.com/img/iknow/exp/global/step_ol_bg.png); font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; visibility: hidden; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"></div><div class=\"content-list-text\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">那怎么切换到中文输入法呢？按快捷键【Ctrl + Space】即可，其中“Space”就是空格键。需要注意的是，必须有输入窗口，此快捷键才会有效。所谓的输入窗口就是可以输入文字的窗口，例如打开的文本文件、终端中等。按下【Ctrl + Space】后，在桌面上的右上方就会显示一个拼音的“拼”字，，如下图所示：</p></div><div class=\"content-list-media\" style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 'Microsoft Yahei', 微软雅黑, arial, 宋体, sans-serif;\"><div class=\"content-list-image clearfix\" style=\"zoom: 1; position: relative; padding: 10px 0px;\"><a class=\"exp-image-wraper\" href=\"http://jingyan.baidu.com/album/da1091fb3e7f8a027849d681.html?picindex=7\" target=\"_self\" style=\"text-decoration: none; color: rgb(45, 100, 179); position: relative; display: block; float: left;\"><img class=\"exp-image-default\" alt=\"CentOS 6.6 如何启用中文输入法\" src=\"quiver-image-url/C46EF754B8785957BA0607B54894F04E.png\" style=\"border: 0px; display: block;\" width=\"375\" height=\"252\"><span class=\"exp-album-enter-mask\" style=\"position: absolute; left: 0px; right: 0px; top: 0px; bottom: 0px; background-color: rgb(51, 51, 51); opacity: 0; cursor: pointer;\"></span></a><div><br></div></div></div><div style=\"clear: both;\"></div></li></ol></div></div></div>"
    }
  ]
}